{"type":null,"faqId":44393,"title":"如何为联系人设置头像？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.06875in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>存储在 SIM 卡中的联系人不支持设置头像，仅支持为存储在手机中的联系人设置头像。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>进入联系人详情界面，点击联系人头像位置。选择一种图片来源，根据屏幕提示调整图片并保存设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>也可以通过“图库”或“文件管理”中的图片设置联系人头像：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>打开要设置为联系人头像的图片，打开选项菜单，在更多选项中点击“设置为 &gt; 联系人照片”，选择手机中存储的联系人，根据屏幕提示调整图片并保存设置。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9893","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400634000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":5,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"联系人,设置头像","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}